{
  "stem": "1704.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you don't answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't go into that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But seeing he had a star, you know, it attracted those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took us to an ice cream parlor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we took the-- my girlfriends home, and he took me home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how it started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Normally, you know, I wouldn't pick up anyone from the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wouldn't have done that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this time it was different, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everything was very intense at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and as it had to be, I had neighbors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his uncle, I'll tell you later about him, he was married to a lady who used to live next door.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the first night when he-- when I met him, he went to them and made inquiries about me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He never proposed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It all went automatically really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, we just went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I got my calling-up papers, and I thought I had to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we just bought a ring, and we were engaged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I got a fortnight to wait before I went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it became months.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of my British-- I had British papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, when they were picked up from their homes, or when they had voluntary-- you know, when they got a call up and just had to go, we were going to a theatre, and assembled there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From there, the Germans worked out who had to go and who didn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they were sent to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, every Tuesday, the train would come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, the lights went on, and the lists were read out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people whose name was called out started packing again.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
